  "title": "6723 - Project Manager (Commercial Entrance Solution)",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Project Manager (Commercial Entrance Solution) </strong></h3><ul><li><strong>$5,500 - $6,500+ Car Allowance + Petrol Card + Season Parking</strong></li><li><strong>5 days - 8.30am to 5.30pm</strong></li><li><strong>Office Location: Ubi</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Manage end-to-end project delivery, ensuring scope, schedule, and budget compliance.</li><li>Establish effective communication channels with customers, internal teams, and third-party vendors.</li><li>Prepare and present clear status reports for different audiences, including executive management.</li><li>Develop and maintain realistic project schedules, considering dependencies and resources.</li><li>Proactively identify and resolve project issues.</li><li>Build strong relationships with customers and provide timely updates on initiatives and concerns.</li><li>Perform other duties as assigned.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or bachelor’s degree required.</li><li>Minimum 2 years in Project Management, preferably in construction projects</li><li>Experience in test planning, implementation, installation and ability to manage multiple complex projects simultaneously.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><br /><strong>📲Interested candidates, please WhatsApp your resume to: +65 9642 0989 (Han) 📧 Or email your resume to: </strong><a href=\"https://employer.mycareersfuture.gov.sg/jobs/6723-senior-hr-executive-education-sector-marine-parade-35k%E2%80%934k-hr-lifecycle-er-supreme-hr-advisory-f4d18bea51dfbe07dff1bccc5ef1e127/view#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">supreme.cc.han@gmail.com</a><strong></strong></p><p><strong>👤Chaw Chiaw Han | R22106723🏢 The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd | EA 14C7279</strong></p>",
